{
  "text": "Thank you. Can you tell me— can you interpret a transmission from \"The Nine, \" where they say \"CH is a principle which is the revealing principle of knowledge and law? \" Can you tell me what that principle is? I am Ra. The principle so veiled in that statement is but the simple principle of the constant or Creator and the transient or the incarnate being and the yearning existing between the two, one for the other, in love and light amidst the distortions of free will acting upon the illusion-bound entity.",
